org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.model
Class DynNetworkSnapshotImpl<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.model.DynNetworkSnapshotImpl<T>
Type Parameters:
T -
All Implemented Interfaces:
DynNetworkSnapshot<T>
public final class DynNetworkSnapshotImpl<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements DynNetworkSnapshot<T>

DynNetworkSnapshotImpl implements all methods to investigate a network in time snapshots within the given time interval. It's computationally intensive, and should be used only when it is not sufficient to search for time intervals only.

Author:
sabina
